{"id": "1411879739853111327", "channel_id": "1411879739853111327", "type": 0, "author_id": "885882671899746305", "author_name": "_cwz_", "author_bot": false, "content": "我來賺點銀芯诶嘿\nID: 100698939\n\n首先是一些密契的風味文字，很多英文也有押韻喔\n\n### 【密契】機械降神\n\n齒輪的轟鳴，神明的降臨。\n鋼鐵的外衣，機械的表皮。\n冰冷的意志，眾生的低吟。\nThe roar of gears, the god unseen.\nA shell of steel, a skin machine.\nA will of frost, the mortals keen.\n\n### 【密契】扭曲雙子·白\n\n祂微笑，你沉陷。\n白色雙子贈你溫柔、予你安眠。\nIt smiles, you sink.\nThe White Twin grants you grace, and bids you rest.\n\n### 【密契】扭曲雙子·黑\n\n祂凝視，你湮滅。\n黑色雙子賜你力量、引你忘卻。\nIt gazes, you wane.\nThe Black Twin grants you power, but bids you forget.\n\n### 【密契】埋骨地絮語\n\n埋葬的不是骨，而是未竟的夢。\nBuried are not bones, but unfinished dreams.\n\n### 【密契】無垢啟示錄\n\n「神國永恆」\n它記載著某個國度的過去、現在與未來。\n\"The Realm endures\"\nIt records the past, present and future of a realm.\n\n### 【密契】海歸線\n\n一段傳說，一朵浪花；\n一名遊子，一紙約定。\nA tale told, a wave born;\na wanderer, a vow sworn.\n\n### 【密契】四月禮讚\n\n三月花開，張燈結彩\n四月花開，繁花似海\n五月花開，昔人不再\nMarch blooms, lanterns burn bright.\nApril blooms, a sea of blossoms white.\nMay blooms, yet the old have vanished from sight.\n\n〈釵頭鳳‧四月〉\n施粉黛，綰蕙蘭，去年巳月燈千盞。\n醉虹霓，艷江南，春色連空，競沒湖畔，漫！漫！漫！\n牡丹綻，芳心亂，今欲賞花花已殘。\n塵緣斷，君未返，悽愴悲惋，情思淚潸，嘆！嘆！嘆！\n\n---\n\n最後是一些自創刻印\n\n### 鍛造\n\n打出後選擇X張抽/棄牌堆的牌升級\n\n### 治癒\n\n打出後回復X點生命\n\n### 預備\n\n使附加的牌獲得保留、預備X\n\n### 抵抗\n\n打出後抵抗下X次獲得的負面效果", "timestamp": "2025-09-01T01:06:01.438000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-01T01:24:37.703000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1411879740473741384", "filename": "Forging.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 8225, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879740473741384/Forging.png?ex=69cbc6b9&is=69ca7539&hm=78612ac0d4746883d1d06dddb3a1189b68055be8e668594b6904e9afdd957483&"}, {"id": "1411879740998160565", "filename": "Healing.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 9997, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879740998160565/Healing.png?ex=69cbc6b9&is=69ca7539&hm=52d93ff9b8d8a2a2bacd0fd1bd7a01acbbe78e0ab73626c9895cb787f01d29c0&"}, {"id": "1411879741644079195", "filename": "Prepare.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 9082, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879741644079195/Prepare.png?ex=69cbc6b9&is=69ca7539&hm=9f92966ee9ac19490b511620c6b9f4b74abf5b7ad8fbacbee73cebc58b8e7772&"}, {"id": "1411879742105325598", "filename": "Resistance.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 11813, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879742105325598/Resistance.png?ex=69cbc6b9&is=69ca7539&hm=9e811cc05ac5631a84b96149d3cadd3b3c9dc988a9755ead611d7b5b4656aba1&"}, {"id": "1411879742583607419", "filename": "AdvForging.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 15109, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879742583607419/AdvForging.png?ex=69cbc6ba&is=69ca753a&hm=c88660af237ba0ee1c2359041eff1d9d1f9a72174b68f91759e696db233388f1&"}, {"id": "1411879742944313354", "filename": "AdvHealing.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 15251, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879742944313354/AdvHealing.png?ex=69cbc6ba&is=69ca753a&hm=9855b8bb75c1d7a43c174d06f0b87079895d582df24e8f6dbd98b94da974afba&"}, {"id": "1411879743388782683", "filename": "AdvPrepare.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 14901, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879743388782683/AdvPrepare.png?ex=69cbc6ba&is=69ca753a&hm=80f7eafac381ae86d89cebf4301b68c9fa485043e062b5e386266e31f2f32294&"}, {"id": "1411879743745429646", "filename": "AdvResistance.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 15937, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411879739853111327/1411879743745429646/AdvResistance.png?ex=69cbc6ba&is=69ca753a&hm=d1aff2810a2456939b9ca3ba545dadde5748815e13d734700c91056efae5a4ad&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411879739853111327", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "刻印模組的副產物", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1395992145638330368", "1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1411881009971990610", "channel_id": "1411879739853111327", "type": 0, "author_id": "885882671899746305", "author_name": "_cwz_", "author_bot": false, "content": "無垢啟示錄是銀河新星寫的，我只加了「神國永恆」四個字以及翻成英文\n海歸線是十三月新聞台寫的，我改了量詞(原本都是「個」)以及翻成英文\n四月禮讚銀河新星寫了「四月花開，昔人不再」，我把它擴展成3句以及翻成英文\n\n除了上述算是合作之外全部都可以算是我創作的\n（那個釵頭鳳我突然心血來潮隨便填的，要押平仄太難了，文采下降了<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> ）\n\n注：翻成英文的部分有GPT輔助，主要是讓他列出有哪些押韻的詞可以用", "timestamp": "2025-09-01T01:11:04.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-01T01:13:25.628000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411879739853111327", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "刻印模組的副產物", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1395992145638330368", "1182359773723754537", "1182359790249332756"]}
